videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle takes an open lane to the basket and demolishes the rim with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Battle elevates for monster jam

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu throws down a wide open dunk to start the second half for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Syracuse opens 2nd half with Chukwu slam

videos.description: Jeremy Harris hits a wide-open 3 to give Buffalo their first lead of the game vs Syracuse.
videos.headline: Buffalo takes 1st lead of game on 3

videos.description: Montell McRae gets the steal on one end, then tosses it to CJ Massinburg for the and-1 in crunch time.
videos.headline: Buffalo goes coast-to-coast for and-1

videos.description: Jeremy Harris hits an important 3, then CJ Massinburg follows with a jumper on the ensuing possession.
videos.headline: Buffalo extends lead on back-to-back clutch shots
